[{"Id": 1016369, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "Sayyid bin Taoos said: Imam has 2 rakats of prayer, in every rakat he recites <Surah Fateha> till “IYYAA-KA NA’BODOO WA IYYAA-KA NASTA-EE’N” he would repeat the verse 100 times, after that he completes the Surah and recites <Surah Ikhlaas> after it. After the prayer he would recite dua <Allahumma Azomal Bala>. This Namaz is highly effective to disperse calamities, and to remove hardships and difficulties.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Marhoom Syed Ibne Taoos farmate hai keh yeh Namaz 2 rakat hai, har rakat mein <Surah Fateha> 1 martaba padhe, aur jab aayat “IYYAA-KA NA’BODOO WA IYYAA-KA NASTA-EE’N” par pohonche to usey 100 martaba padhe aur surah tamaam karne ke baad <Surah Ikhlaas> 1 martaba padhe. Yeh Namaz balaawo’n aur waqte mushkilaat se najaat ke liye bohot mufid hai.", "UrduDescription": "مرحوم سید بن طاوؤس فرماتے ہیں یہ نماز بھی ۲ رکعت ہے <سورۂ فاتحہ> کو پڑھے جب (ایاک نعبد و ایاک نستعین) تک پہنچے اس وقت ۱۰۰ مرتبہ (ایاک نعبد و ایاک نستعین) کو پڑھے اس کے بعد سورہ کو تمام کرے اس کے بعد ایک دفعہ <سورۂ اخلاص> کو پڑھے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "Arab